# Keep the ATC Docker build context (the monorepo root) small + deterministic.
# The Dockerfile explicitly COPYs only what it needs from catalogit,
# agent-runtime, and ask-the-code; this file blocks accidental inclusion of
# already-built / per-developer artifacts and packages the image doesn't need.

**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.git
**/.idea
**/.vscode
**/coverage
**/.DS_Store

# Test-only artifacts.
**/test-integration

# Per-package artifacts that shouldn't ride into the image.
**/.session-handoff*.md
**/.npmrc
**/.env*

# The Dockerfile itself doesn't need to be COPYd inside the image.
agents/ask-the-code/Dockerfile

# Local-dev / packages unrelated to the ATC image.
docker-compose.yml
README.md
docs/
agents/bump-it/
infra/
tooling/
